f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，仲好意思講通識，係你哋之前要推行，而家話係老師教既問題，不如你話班學生學得有問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔少學校有藍到黑既老師，日日講中國點好點好，班學生咪又係當個啲老師智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947346f65e774e3662eb49ee2bccb96a072caafe","tid":1802759,"uid":212168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"呢d冚家剷正宗賣港狗賊  連自己母語都出賣"},{"pid":"2f04399ee94bb852c4abeaafbcf1b694ce06d37a","tid":1802759,"uid":253479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:19:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1526d2e92ba6a225e6664eec6e30864221d368c","tid":1802759,"uid":9253,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:19:53.000Z","msg":"你老母啦 不如唔好教中文 直接教英文啦 咁咪唔會有人唔識英文囉"},{"pid":"ba849a3a7c5e9e5d6d9c2c735dccd1745d6ce68d","tid":1802759,"uid":55835,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"947346f65e774e3662eb49ee2bccb96a072caafe","tid":1802759,"uid":212168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"呢d冚家剷正宗賣港狗賊  連自己母語都出賣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:21:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要迎合市場，我all in英文 唔好？<br />\n去強國大把囡囡一聽到「sorry, I can only speak English 」<br />\n<br />\n立即出哂水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></s